metadata.title: Husqvarna 545081832 Leaf Blower Engine Gasket Set Genuine Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) Part
description: Genuine Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) parts! This engine gasket set (part number 545081832) is for leaf blowers. Engine gasket set 545081832 includes the major gaskets to replace when rebuilding the engine. Let the engine cool before installing this part. Wear work gloves to protect your hands. For Craftsman, Poulan, Weed Eater, & Mcculloch.
